18:35.414 --> 18:37.383
(quietly):
Listen, you guys, you really...

18:37.516 --> 18:39.951
ALL:
Got to get a name.

18:41.287 --> 18:43.414
Okay, so you'll be able
to get the tow truck here

18:43.556 --> 18:44.785
just as soon as you can?

18:44.924 --> 18:46.517
-(wind howling)
- Oh, great.

18:46.659 --> 18:47.626
Uh-huh.

18:47.760 --> 18:49.956
- Oh, yeah, great.
- Where is everybody?

18:50.096 --> 18:52.587
Uh, excuse me. Well, uh,
they went back in Ralph's car.

18:52.732 --> 18:54.131
Mine broke down.

18:54.266 --> 18:57.259
-(wind howling) -Yeah, right,
I'm at the Blue Ox Inn, and...

18:57.403 --> 18:59.633
- Pretend we're together.
- Lori Beth, what is

18:59.772 --> 19:01.501
your problem?

19:01.640 --> 19:03.700
- That's the problem.
- Huh? Well, e-excuse me.

19:03.843 --> 19:05.936
Yeah. Right.
Yeah, yeah, I got to go.

19:06.078 --> 19:07.739
Thanks a lot. Bye.

19:07.880 --> 19:09.609
Ah. Hey, you country guys
are real nice.

19:09.749 --> 19:11.979
Yeah, I just talked to a guy,
Jed, do you know him?

19:12.118 --> 19:13.517
- He's a wonderful guy.
- Richie... (chuckles)

19:13.652 --> 19:17.214
he wants to pull me
through the snow by my hair.

19:17.356 --> 19:18.585
Come on outside, little lady.

19:18.724 --> 19:20.818
-(gasps) -You and me
got some funning to do.

19:20.960 --> 19:22.120
Hey, wait a minute!

19:22.261 --> 19:24.389
You can't just carry off
my girl like that.

19:24.530 --> 19:27.056
Are you with this
skinny little guy?

19:27.199 --> 19:28.861
Yeah, she's with
this skinny little guy!

19:29.001 --> 19:31.868
And you better put her down
right now or else, bucko!

19:32.004 --> 19:34.940
Oh, boy, a fight.

19:35.074 --> 19:37.566
I thought I was
gonna have to go all night

19:37.710 --> 19:39.906
without getting
to punch some heads in.

19:41.881 --> 19:43.747
-(wind howling) -FONZIE:
Whoa, let me tell you something,

19:43.883 --> 19:46.875
Ralph's car is broken down,
you know? Uh...

19:47.019 --> 19:48.885
What are you doing, Red?

19:49.021 --> 19:50.580
He's shaking me, Fonz.

19:50.723 --> 19:51.747
Wait, wait! Whoa!

19:51.891 --> 19:53.051
I'm glad you're here.

19:53.192 --> 19:56.184
You picked a fight
with a red and black tree?

19:59.098 --> 20:01.032
Here, this'll help even it up.

20:01.167 --> 20:03.192
Wait a minute,
I don't want to play with this.

20:03.335 --> 20:05.327
This is dangerous here.

20:08.374 --> 20:10.274
RICHIE:
Oh.

20:10.409 --> 20:12.173
Oh, Fonz, that was good,
that was good.

20:12.311 --> 20:13.642
Good? The man is a mountain.

20:13.779 --> 20:15.213
What are you talking, good?

20:15.347 --> 20:17.942
All right, hold it, hold it,
hold it, hold it, hold it.

20:18.084 --> 20:20.211
You know what's wrong here?
I'll tell you what's wrong.

20:20.352 --> 20:22.287
I see it now.
You're too tense.

20:22.421 --> 20:25.357
Yeah. Loosen up.
Open those fingers up.

20:25.491 --> 20:26.515
Yeah, shake 'em out.

20:26.659 --> 20:28.183
Don't that feel good! Whoo!

20:28.327 --> 20:31.024
Yeah. Hey, listen, let me ask
you a very important question.

20:31.163 --> 20:32.961
Have you lived here
all your life?

20:33.099 --> 20:34.896
Yeah, I guess.

20:35.034 --> 20:37.161
Have you ever seen
a blue jay in the snow?

20:37.303 --> 20:40.568
I'm talking about a blue jay
with its wings spread out,

20:40.706 --> 20:43.937
nestled... in that
blanket of white, going,

20:44.076 --> 20:47.239
(high-pitched):
"Caw, caw, caw."

20:47.379 --> 20:48.244
Caw?

20:48.380 --> 20:49.780
Yeah, let's go. Come on.

20:49.915 --> 20:52.077
Here we go.
I'll show it to you right now.

20:52.218 --> 20:53.207
There we go.

20:53.352 --> 20:55.514
- Hello.
- Are you sure?

20:55.654 --> 21:00.092
Am I sure? Would ljosh
a very sensitive man like you?

21:00.226 --> 21:02.217
Hey, come on.

21:02.361 --> 21:04.853
Are you nuts?!

21:11.036 --> 21:13.130
Richie, what is going on?

21:13.272 --> 21:14.398
That is great strategy.

21:14.540 --> 21:16.872
See, Fonz is gonna lure
that guy out into the snow.

21:17.009 --> 21:18.738
He's gonna say,
"Here, look at the blue jay."

21:18.878 --> 21:21.278
The guy's gonna look up,
and then whap, hoo, faw!

21:21.413 --> 21:22.904
We're gonna nail that guy.

21:23.048 --> 21:24.311
Richie, he's so big!

21:24.450 --> 21:26.316
Yeah. But not for the two of us.

21:26.452 --> 21:27.510
I think.

21:27.653 --> 21:29.087
(Richie yells)

21:29.221 --> 21:31.053
Richie!

21:38.864 --> 21:40.764
An icicle.

21:40.900 --> 21:42.766
Boy, look
